主要翻译
 
the Resurrection n (religion: rising of Christ)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 耶稣复活 yē sū fù huó TC Traditional Chinese 耶穌復活  (基督教)
 -- Christians celebrate the Resurrection at Easter.
 
resurrection n (person: rising from dead)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 复活 fù huó TC Traditional Chinese 復活  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 重生 fù huó，chóng shēng 
 -- Resurrection is a common theme in horror films.
 
resurrection n figurative (revival: of an idea or custom)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 复兴，重新流行，恢复，死灰复燃 fù xīng ，chóng xīn liú xíng ，huī fù，sǐ huī fù rán TC Traditional Chinese 恢復  (思想等)
 -- Recently here has been a resurrection of Marxist theory on campus.

